    public class AutocompleteArea
extends org.fxmisc.richtext.StyledTextArea<java.lang.Boolean>
    Implementation of a StyledTextArea with autocompletion functionality. Code partially borrowed from MOOC Text Editor project implemented in the course "Data Structures and Performance" by UC San Diego via coursera.org
